GK My Halaba Hotel Management Information System
Business Requirements Document (Version 1.0)
1. Project Title

GK My Halaba Hotel Management Information System & Digital Presence Platform

2. Project Owner

GK My Halaba Hotel

Halaba Kulito, Central Ethiopia

3. System Developer

Israel Aklilu

4th Year Computer Science Student

Graphic Designer | Video Editor | Web & System Developer | Digital Marketing Specialist

4. Background

GK My Halaba Hotel is a newly established luxury hotel located in Halaba Kulito. The hotel provides elegant accommodations, restaurant services, coffee, modern hospitality, and a secure environment for business travelers, tourists, and families.

Although the hotel offers quality services, it currently has no official website and no established digital presence. Customers cannot view room availability online, submit reservations through the web, or explore the hotel's services before visiting.

To address these challenges, the hotel requires a complete digital solution that improves customer experience, streamlines hotel operations, and strengthens its online visibility.

5. Business Problem

The hotel currently faces several challenges:

No official website
No online booking system
No centralized hotel management system
Manual reservation management
Limited online visibility
No digital marketing platform
No centralized customer database
No online payment integration
Limited reporting and analytics
6. Proposed Solution

Develop a complete Hotel Management Information System (HMIS) that includes:

Luxury hotel website
Online reservation system
Admin dashboard
Customer portal
Room management
Guest management
Restaurant management
Gallery
Blog
Payment integration
Reporting system
Multi-language support (English & Amharic)
7. Business Objectives

The project aims to:

Improve customer experience
Increase room reservations
Simplify hotel management
Build a strong online presence
Reduce manual work
Improve communication with guests
Enhance marketing activities
Support future business growth
8. Project Scope
Included
Public website
Online reservation
Room management
Restaurant information
Gallery
Admin dashboard
User authentication
Payment support
Reports
Responsive design
English & Amharic support
Not Included (Version 1)
Mobile application
AI chatbot
Advanced accounting system
HR and payroll management
Inventory management

These can be added in future versions.

